public class PhysicalModelImpl

An implementation of the model object 'Physical Model'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Database Name
  • Database Version
  • Catalog
  • Schema
  • Parent Model
  • Tables
  • Primary Keys
  • Foreign Keys
